# API (NestJS) Rules
- Feature-module structure: `src/<feature>/` with controller, service, dto, entity.
- Validate all input with DTOs (class-validator) once wired in Phase 2.
- Controllers stay thin; business logic lives in services.
- Every module ships unit tests (Vitest). A route is not done without a test.
- Return typed responses; share cross-boundary types via `@easycasa/shared`.
